{"id":288183,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/【图说天朝】莫言家的墙/","date":"2013-04-08T03:03:12Z","modified":"2013-04-08T03:03:12Z","title":"【图说天朝】莫言家的墙","content":"<p>清明期间，山东高密平安庄莫言旧居3天接待了超千人。从去年的“拔萝卜”到现在的“抠墙皮，挖砖块”，持续人流对莫言旧居也造成了一定程度的损害。“墙皮被抠掉一块，他们说是带回去，把土撒到家里沾‘文气’。”莫言二嫂葛金芳说。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/8RRLQ11S00AN0001.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-288184\" alt=\"8RRLQ11S00AN0001\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/8RRLQ11S00AN0001.jpg\" width=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/8RRLQ11S00AN0001.jpg 980w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/04/8RRLQ11S00AN0001-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,21627,13770],"tags":[20554,10149]}